{"tid":1071750,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[百年樹木]","createTime":"2019-03-21T14:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T18:34:31.000Z","uid":223818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8be7c1f985e4ebafc0e2b660ebc97101e6f2c822","tid":1071750,"uid":223818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T14:23:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QE1piGBS1sI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQE1piGBS1sI&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3J1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=aafb97f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QE1piGBS1sI</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完feel到歌詞同PV都有d意思<br />\n想用pv做藍本寫下文<br />\n入嚟放低你嘅諗法！"},{"pid":"c5f81ffb89c24b3c0d20c34bdca8d76b076202e0","tid":1071750,"uid":223818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T14:43:14.000Z","msg":"站在天橋，眺望著車來車往的馬路<br />\n突然手機一震 打算查看時<br />\n&ldquo;喂！&rdquo; 女朋友輕輕從樓梯口呼喚我<br />\n我急忙收起手機 轉身 看見了一身中學校服的少女<br />\n&ldquo;咁樣得唔得架？&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;你轉個身嚟睇下&rdquo;<br />\n少女照辦了<br />\n&ldquo;得啊&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;我都唔係你地d學生，咁樣著你地d校服唔係咁好囉...&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;咁我學校搞個party啊嘛，你緊係要襯我啦下話？&rdquo;我理所當然地道。<br />\n今天是5C班的十五週年聚會，我也不清楚為何我要帶上女朋友，讓他束起馬尾，十足中學時代的少女&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n沒錯，也許我也只是想令妳妒忌。<br />\n只是..為了遮掩自己的自卑，只是如此。<br />\n不過這一切也不過是個幻想<br />\n妳早已不知去向，我也許也不再重要。<br />\n我不願接受著自己內心想法地拖起女朋友的手，向馬路走去。"},{"pid":"95945bdc57db0829cfa101b8857ec50e6649d2f7","tid":1071750,"uid":142331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T16:05:41.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n想睇除咗mv 以外嘅情節<br />\nbtw 樓主啲排板可以好少少 而家睇得有啲辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a206ea4ca8941df1bee8a8b8662c0709768f2d18","tid":1071750,"uid":234578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T16:09:02.000Z","msg":"會唔會考慮想埋歲月同裝睡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2994959f86d78f6365e849325ce9be5f58d9e01","tid":1071750,"uid":234578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re